column17:
Product Description

Excited by Ted Lapidus is a Aromatic Green fragrance for men. Excited was launched in 2004. The nose behind this fragrance is Gerard Anthony. Top notes are pine tree and kumquat; middle notes are cyclamen patchouli and jasmine; base notes are sandalwood amber white musk and brazilian rosewood.
